N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 40.40 - Liquidation

State Regulations

Upon the termination of this Part, the commissioner shall
dispose of all funds received hereunder in an equitable manner, together with
claims to any such funds which are unpaid and owing at the time of termination
and which are in accordance with the intent of the act and the provisions of
this Part. Notes
